==機制==
許多問題都可能導致頭暈，因為身體的許多部位都是身體能否維持平衡的必要條件（例如：[[內耳|內耳]]、[[眼睛|眼睛]]、[[肌肉|肌肉]]、[[骨骼|骨骼]]、和[[中樞神經系統|中樞神經系統]]）。
<ref name=merck>{{cite web |title=Dizziness and Vertigo |year=2009 |publisher=Merck Manual |url=http://www.merck.com/mmpe/sec08/ch084/ch084e.html?qt=dizziness&alt=sh |accessdate=2017-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705010644/https://www.merckmanuals.com/professional/ear-nose-and-throat-disorders/approach-to-the-patient-with-ear-problems/dizziness-and-vertigo?qt=dizziness&alt=sh |dead-url=no }}</ref>

常見的頭暈之生理因素：
*腦部的[[血液|血液]]供應不足 →原因：
**[[血壓|血壓]]驟降<ref name=merck />
**[[心臟|心臟]]問題或[[動脈|動脈]]不通<ref name=merck />
*頸椎錯位<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Chu ECP |coauthors=Chin WL |title=Cervicogenic dizziness |journal=Oxford Medical Case Reports |date=2019 Nov |volume=2019 |issue=11 |page=476-478 |doi=10.1093/omcr/omz115 |pmid=31844531 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/31844531/ |accessdate=2020-01-03 |archive-date=2020-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517124811/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/31844531/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*[[失明|失明]]或視野扭曲或{{tsl|en|Visual cues}}。<ref name=merck />
*內耳出問題<ref name=merck />
*中樞神經功能受藥物作用影響，包括但不限於：{{tsl|en|anticonvulsants|抗癲癇藥}}和[[sedatives|鎮靜劑]]。<ref name=merck />
* [[處方藥|處方藥]]的[[副作用|副作用]]，包括但不限於：[[氫離子幫浦阻斷劑|氫離子幫浦阻斷劑]]（PPI）和Coumadin。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fda.gov/Drugs/DrugSafety/ucm245011.htm|title=Drug Safety and Availability - FDA Drug Safety Communication: Low magnesium levels can be associated with long-term use of Proton Pump Inhibitor drugs (PPIs)|first=Center for Drug Evaluation and|last=Research|work=www.fda.gov|access-date=2017-07-11|archive-date=2019-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424012705/https://www.fda.gov/Drugs/DrugSafety/ucm245011.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rxlist.com/coumadin-side-effects-drug-center.htm|title=Common Side Effects of Coumadin (Warfarin Sodium) Drug Center - RxList|publisher=|access-date=2017-07-11|archive-date=2012-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120921012945/http://www.rxlist.com/coumadin-side-effects-drug-center.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

